            <content:encoded>
                <![CDATA[
                    
                    <div class="tougao-user">感谢IT之家网友 <a href="https://m.ithome.com/html/app/open.html?url=ithome%3A%2F%2Fuserpage%3Fid%3D816870" rel="nofollow">Freddy123</a>、<a href="https://m.ithome.com/html/app/open.html?url=ithome%3A%2F%2Fuserpage%3Fid%3D126061" rel="nofollow">rain0218C</a>、<a href="https://m.ithome.com/html/app/open.html?url=ithome%3A%2F%2Fuserpage%3Fid%3D1650036" rel="nofollow">lxylizi</a> 的线索投递！</div>
            <p><a class="s_tag" href="https://www.ithome.com/" target="_blank">IT之家</a> 10 月 28 日消息，苹果今日向 Apple Watch 用户推送了 watchOS 11.1 更新（内部版本号：22R585），本次更新距离上次发布正式版间隔 25 天。</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img height="528" src="https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2024/10/3f1c4362-b733-4eb1-8fad-849e5fa0a036.jpg?x-bce-process=image/format,f_auto" title="苹果 watchOS 11.1 正式发布，海外版新增“睡眠呼吸暂停检测”功能" width="1440" /></p><p>watchOS 11.1 主要面向<strong>海外市场版本</strong>&nbsp;Apple Watch 用户新增“睡眠呼吸暂停检测”功能，该功能适用于 Apple Watch Series 9、Series 10 及 Apple Watch Ultra 2 三款机型。</p><p>当相应呼吸干扰数据显示用户在 30 天内持续出现“中度至重度睡眠窒息症”的迹象时，用户将收到相应警告通知，之后用户可以根据手表提供的健康报告联系医护人员。</p><h3>附 watchOS 11 发布历史：</h3><ul class="custom_reference list-paddingleft-1"><li class="list-undefined list-reference-paddingleft"><p><a class="breakall" href="https://www.ithome.com/0/804/407.htm" target="_blank">2024-10-23：watchOS 11.1 RC (22R582)</a></p></li><li class="list-undefined list-reference-paddingleft"><p><a class="breakall" href="https://www.ithome.com/0/802/262.htm" target="_blank">2024-10-15：watchOS 11.1 Beta 5 (22R5575a)</a></p></li><li class="list-undefined list-reference-paddingleft"><p><a class="breakall" href="https://www.ithome.com/0/800/515.htm" target="_blank">2024-10-08：watchOS 11.1 Beta 4 (22R5569a)</a></p></li><li class="list-undefined list-reference-paddingleft"><p><a class="breakall" href="https://www.ithome.com/0/800/747.htm" target="_blank">2024-10-04：watchOS 11.0.1 (22R361)</a></p></li><li class="list-undefined list-reference-paddingleft"><p><a class="breakall" href="https://www.ithome.com/0/799/834.htm" target="_blank">2024-10-02：watchOS 11.1 Beta 3 (22R5559b)</a></p></li><li class="list-undefined list-reference-paddingleft"><p><a class="breakall" href="https://www.ithome.com/0/797/855.htm" target="_blank">2024-09-24：watchOS 11.1 Beta 2 (22R5554e)</a></p></li><li class="list-undefined list-reference-paddingleft"><p><a class="breakall" href="https://www.ithome.com/0/796/443.htm" target="_blank">2024-09-18：watchOS 11.1 Beta (22R5545g)</a></p></li><li class="list-undefined list-reference-paddingleft"><p><a class="breakall" href="https://www.ithome.com/0/796/325.htm" target="_blank">2024-09-17：watchOS 11 (22R349)</a></p></li><li class="list-undefined list-reference-paddingleft"><p><a class="breakall" href="https://www.ithome.com/0/794/654.htm" target="_blank">2024-09-10：watchOS 11 RC (22R349)</a></p></li><li class="list-undefined list-reference-paddingleft"><p><a class="breakall" href="https://www.ithome.com/0/789/915.htm" target="_blank">2024-08-21：watchOS 11 Beta 7 (22R5348a)</a></p></li><li class="list-undefined list-reference-paddingleft"><p><a class="breakall" href="https://www.ithome.com/0/788/033.htm" target="_blank">2024-08-13：watchOS 11 Beta 6 (22R5340a)</a></p></li><li class="list-undefined list-reference-paddingleft"><p><a class="breakall" href="https://www.ithome.com/0/786/428.htm" target="_blank">2024-08-06：watchOS 11 Beta 5 (22R5328e)</a></p></li><li class="list-undefined list-reference-paddingleft"><p><a class="breakall" href="https://www.ithome.com/0/783/800.htm" target="_blank">2024-07-24：watchOS 11 Beta 4 (22R5318h)</a></p></li><li class="list-undefined list-reference-paddingleft"><p><a class="breakall" href="https://www.ithome.com/0/780/489.htm" target="_blank">2024-07-09：watchOS 11 Beta 3 (22R5309f)</a></p></li><li class="list-undefined list-reference-paddingleft"><p><a class="breakall" href="https://www.ithome.com/0/774/341.htm" target="_blank">2024-06-11：watchOS 11 Beta (22R5284o)</a></p></li><li class="list-undefined list-reference-paddingleft"><p><a class="breakall" href="https://www.ithome.com/0/777/406.htm" target="_blank">2024-06-11：watchOS 11 Beta 2 (22R5299d)</a></p></li></ul><p>IT之家小伙伴如果找到更多新内容，可以在投稿或评论区中提出你的发现~<img src="https://img.ithome.com/images/svg/emoji/rm_e_weixiao.svg" title="苹果 watchOS 11.1 正式发布，海外版新增“睡眠呼吸暂停检测”功能" width="20" /> </p><p class="ad-tips">广告声明：文内含有的对外跳转链接（包括不限于超链接、二维码、口令等形式），用于传递更多信息，节省甄选时间，结果仅供参考，IT之家所有文章均包含本